Redesign the entire sidebar navigation system to be modern, adaptive, and enterprise-grade with support for collapsed mode, tooltips, animations, and improved UX.

---

## 1. Sidebar Layout Upgrade

Implement two states:

### Expanded Mode (default)
- Width: 240px
- Show icons + labels
- Section headers (Workspace, Service, Manage)

### Collapsed Mode
- Width: 72px
- Show only icons
- Hide labels
- Enable tooltip on hover

Add toggle button in topbar:
- Icon: hamburger/menu
- Persist state (localStorage)

