## 2. Sidebar Item Redesign

### Default State
- Transparent background
- Text: muted (opacity 70%)
- Icon: neutral color

### Hover State
- Background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08)
- Text: white
- Icon: #a78bfa
- Smooth transition (0.2s)
- Slight scale effect (1.02)

### Active State
- Background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(139,92,246,0.2), rgba(59,130,246,0.15))
- Border-left: 3px solid #8b5cf6
- Text: white
- Icon: #8b5cf6
- Glow effect: subtle inner shadow

---

## 3. Tooltip System (IMPORTANT)

When sidebar is collapsed:

- On hover over icon:
  - Show tooltip on right side
  - Content: menu name (e.g., "Dashboard", "Tickets")

### Tooltip Design:
- Background: #111827 (dark)
- Text: white
- Padding: 6px 10px
- Border-radius: 6px
- Font-size: 12px
- Shadow: soft (0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.3))
- Position: right-center of icon

### Behavior:
- Delay: 150ms
- Fade-in animation
- Hide on mouse leave

